cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "Library-First Engineering (LFE)"
message: "If you use Library-First Engineering or build on it, please cite it."
type: software
authors:
  - given-names: Stylianos
    family-names: Chiotis
repository-code: "https://github.com/StChiotis/Library-First-Engineering"
abstract: >-
  A file-driven, persona-based framework for building production software
  with AI agents — language-agnostic, IDE-agnostic, LLM-agnostic. LFE keeps
  agentic AI reliable across sessions by keeping the human on the wheel,
  treating documentation as the source of truth, and coordinating every
  pipeline step through physical files instead of conversation memory.
keywords:
  - library-first-engineering
  - agentic-ai
  - ai-reliability
  - llm
  - software-engineering-process
license: MIT
